      "content": "Yeah, the \"gotcha\" part is what worries me most. It feels like there could be all sorts of little hidden problems lurking in there that I can't see. Is there a way to describe how these kinds of clauses basically \"hide\" risks? It feels like they are intentionally trying to be sneaky.",
